of the farmers work only 10 per cent of irrigated land. See IFAD, Syrian Arab Republic, Country 
Strategic Opportunities Programme, 2009.   
</p>
<p> 34 See IFAD, ibid. 
 35 Samir Aita, &#8220;Labour markets policies and institutions&#8221;, pp. 2, 19 and 21.  
